[166.004859, "o", "                                                   \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[8;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[2m\u001b[36m- Run: `python src/cli.py World` (add `--shout` to upper-case).\u001b[0m                                            \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[9;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[2m\u001b[36m- Test: `pytest -q`\u001b[0m                                                                                        \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[10;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[2m\u001b[36m- Lint: `ruff check src/`\u001b[0m                                                                                  \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[11;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[2m\u001b[36m\u001b[0m                                                                                                           \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[12;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[2m\u001b[36m## Conventions\u001b[0m                                                                                             \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[13;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[2m\u001b[36m- Python 3, standard library only (argparse).\u001b[0m                                                              \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[14;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[2"]
[166.004881, "o", "m\u001b[36m- Logic split into small single-purpose modules (`util`, `formatters`).\u001b[0m                                    \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[15;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[2m\u001b[36m- Tests live in `tests/`, import from `src.`, and target pure functions.\u001b[0m                                   \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[16;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[2m\u001b[36m\u001b[0m                                                                                                           \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[17;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[2m\u001b[36m## Architecture\u001b[0m                                                                                            \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[18;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[2m\u001b[36m- `src/cli.py` — entrypoint; builds the argparse parser, wires `util` + `formatters`, prints the result.\u001b[0m   \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[19;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[2m\u001b[36m- `src/util.py` — `format_greeting(name, shout=False)` builds the greeting string.\u001b[0m                         \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[20;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[2m\u001b[36m- `src/formatters.py` — `render(greeting, fmt=\"text\")` output formatter; tex"]
