[166.022134, "o", "                                    \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[2m\u001b[36m- Logic split into small single-purpose modules (`util`, `formatters`).\u001b[0m                                    \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[2m\u001b[36m- Tests live in `tests/`, import from `src.`, and target pure functions.\u001b[0m                                   \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[2m\u001b[36m\u001b[0m                                                                                                           \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[2m\u001b[36m## Architecture\u001b[0m                                                                                            \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[2m\u001b[36m- `src/cli.py` — entrypoint; builds the argparse parser, wires `util` + `formatters`, prints the result.\u001b[0m   \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[2m\u001b[36m- `src/util.py` — `format_greeting(name, shout=False)` builds the greeting string.\u001b[0m                         \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[2m\u001b[36m- `src/formatters.py` — `render(greeting, fmt=\"text\")` output fo"]
[166.022168, "o", "rmatter; text-only today, raises on unkno…\u001b[0m \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[2m\u001b[36m- Flow: cli → format_greeting → render → stdout.\u001b[0m                                                           \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[2m\u001b[36m\u001b[0m                                                                                                           \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[2m\u001b[36m## Glossary\u001b[0m                                                                                                \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[2m\u001b[36m- **greet** — the CLI program / project name.\u001b[0m                                                              \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[2m\u001b[36m- **shout** — flag that upper-cases the greeting output.\u001b[0m                                                   \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[2m\u001b[36m- **render** — formatter step; text-only today, `--format json` is on the roadmap.\u001b[0m                         \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m                                                       "]
